            <title>[FLINK-2082] Chained stream tasks share the same RuntimeContext</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2082</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Chained stream operators currently share the same runtimecontext, this will certainly lead to problems in the future. &lt;/p&gt;

